reviewText: I like movies Latin cinema, but I feel that the movie has no force, need more strength in all, are not fully exposed the social and political problem that exists in these southern countries , in the movie not it is included the problem full of jail; not is movie gay although has some nuances, stayed in mediocrity, I give three star.
